{"tid":2511750,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（唔是免費）有兩隻好可愛嘅肥婆熊仔鼠等人要","createTime":"2021-05-01T06:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T06:50:00.000Z","uid":395446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"72aebb2693bd55a85db52f5d8269ac731ca3e8a9","tid":2511750,"uid":395446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"自家繁殖熊仔鼠兩隻想搵人領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為最近好多啲虐待寵物嘅新聞<br />\n好擔心鼠鼠會遇到壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想附加一啲條件比領養者<br />\n<br />\n一：希望領養者曾經養過<br />\n二：唔洗錢領養驚畀人拎去餵其他爬蟲類, 所以每一隻會收返300蚊，全數捐畀612 funding<br />\n三：領養者可以定期更新鼠鼠狀況<br />\n四：每人限領養一隻<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就pm我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPS8NXi4vxziH5RTQcdSKaTTQkRfaMPbJPUq117jg8U85?filename=Q9L0ai3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9L0ai3.png&h=ca6fcca8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3ACgmeZqUgocryaCF84eM1aJTgm4UXi5QussZQLSebf?filename=2cbnoD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cbnoD7.png&h=3bf39274&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}